{"id":"5798","title":"极品公子","writer":"烽火戏诸侯","dateline":"1436968964","updatetime":"1436968964","isover":"1","filesize":"8977238","linecount":"76810","wordcount":"2860723","imgpath":"https://ae01.alicdn.com/kf/UTB8c42Lv0nJXKJkSaiyq6AhwXXaA.jpg","hash":"jipingongzi","urlhash":"","sign":"","desc":"讲述一个不学无术纨绔子弟成长为一代枭雄、黑道太子、金融教皇的历程！,钱，他将继承一个超过百亿美元资产庞大家族的财产，多得可以当用美金当纸烧；貌，他妈妈是省花，爸爸是风流倜傥，长得堪称女人的“杀手”；既然上帝如此慷慨赋予身为两个庞大家族第三代中唯一的男性公民的他这么多，他还有什么理由不去征服美女――上帝送给男人的最好礼物？,当然，玩温柔玩得厌烦的时候，他可以玩玩血腥,玩女人玩得失去激情时，他可以玩玩阴谋诡计，可以堆积木一样搭建他的金融帝国！你可以叫他小人、色狼、淫贼、人渣，或者黑道魁首、金融教皇、败类……不过他喜欢称自己为――花花公子！以征服美女为终身目标而奋斗！,既然身为黑道太子，为什么不炸掉什么狗日的靖国神社替华夏族出口气呢？既然是金融教皇，那为什么不给嚣张跋扈的美国制造一场金融风暴呢？,虽然讲述的是一个花花公子的风流生活，但绝对“色而不淫”！,","hot":"5582","num":"1190000","cid":"58","suggcate":"都市小说,言情都市","suggcids":"69,285","notbook":"0","fetchv":"0","lasthot":"1477336078","clicknum":"225","isvip":"0","ish":"1","age":"现代","channel":"女","isqiniu":"1","list":"0,5zl,bav,h20,np9,tqg,ypk,15fm,1bsg,1huy,1nm9,1sj1,1x85,21yn,274t,2co3,2hkz,2lrm,2qfh,2v88,2z9a,33dk,37go,3aum,3dur,3guu,3ko9,3ohp,3rkj,3uqz,3xin,431n,4790,4aog,4ext,4hwr,4ld2,4olc,4t4l,4xfi,51ne,56ld,5b3s,5foo,5itg,5n7g,5rbn,5wcr,605g,618m,64n6,68jz,6cn1,6g4c,6ki6,6o8c,6t2n,6wyh,70i7,74rd,787g,7bni,7eyb,7ij5,7mrm,7qmw,7uwu,7ypo,83j8,874x,8bnp,8g6o,8kik,8oop,8sx5,8xxo,92iy,96xs,9b3k,9f44,9jgj,9npa,9t72,9xji,a23i,a67d,abd2,ag0m,ajub,anag,aqyl,avx1,b01g,b3uk,b8sa,be4b,bhus,blvu,bq8x,bu00,bxua,c267,c5fj,c9nr,ce56,ciux,co3h,ct0c,cxso,d2wn,d7bc,dbxl,dgpr,dkj0,dobi,drpd,dvdz,dzg7,e2wa,e6ve,eb0z,efaq,eiuq,emty,eqxa,ev0n,ez5a,f3hg,f7j7,fbop,ffng,fjmg,fo8h,fsl9,fxkd,g26n,g754,gbmx,gg0t,gkue,gpis,gumu,gzg1,h4dw,h9fu,hf3l,hjqg,hp2q,hugo,hzla,i51i,ia9q,ifdz,ikho,ioo0,isuz,iykx,j3ay,j7vc,jc0e,jgj4,jl33,jpgu,juy0,jzwk,k5ce,kag5,kfkd,kk5u,kou9,ktq4,kyk8,l49a,l93a,lebs,lj0v,lnuz,lske,lxb5,m1v7,m5ir,m9hx,mdpw,mi8q,mmjn,mrii,mvm1,mzny,n40h,n865,nby8,ngw7,nld4,nq4j,nvhk,o030,o4yn,o8xm,odqj,ohvm,omlq,orr2,ovyd,p124,p2cw,p6hj,pbdu,pg8l,piwo,pn6f,ps7f,px9r,q29p,q7e8,qbyc,qg1u,qkqz,qpao,qtot,qz5i,r3uh,r8ry,rdu